Feature engineering:

Reference from : The must-know mathematics and statistics behind AI (pre-requisite mentored session)
Author: Yogesh Singh (Yogi's Data Lab)

It is a technique where in the data variables or labels are transformed from one form in to another form based on a certain logic.
Need for doing feature engineering is for model to better get trained and predict / provide an output.

Benefits

1) Better generalization
2) Improved model accuracy
3) Enhanced Interpretability.

Well explained
